Text: RE TennisBen Ive got a pulled muscle groin that Ive been trying to nurse for a few months Went for a run this weekend and strained it I wonder if we could either postpone tennis for a week or so If you prefer I could but will have to take it fairly easy Let me know Dave Original Message From SMTP Sent Friday July AM To Yeager David Subject RE Tennis Tuesday sounds good Does around pm work for you Original Message From Yeager David David lPasocomENRON Sent Friday July AM To Rogers Benjamin Subject RE Tennis Ben good to hear from you How about Tuesday Monday would also probably work Let me know what is best for you Dave Original Message From Rogers Benjamin SMTPBenjamin NRONcom Sent Friday July AM To Yeager David Subject Tennis David Wanted to see when you wanted to get together for a little tennis and a couple of beers afterwards Next week is pretty open for me except Wednesday This weekend is out because I am headed to Barton Creek for a little golf weekend Hope all is going well and Ill talk to you soon Ben This email and any files transmitted with it from the ElPaso Corporation are confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom they are addressed If you have received this email in error please notify the sender This email and any files transmitted with it from the ElPaso Corporation are confidential and intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom they are addressed If you have received this email in error please notify the sender
